      "description": {
        "text": "=General= A large boulder and a wall. There are also several other boulders nearby. =Directions= Drive down Vårdsätravägen through Hågadalen, then turn right across the bridge and park immediately on the left. Cross the road and follow the bridleway towards Predikstolen crag. The boulder is about 50 metres before the crag, and the wall is above the crag. =Sectors=",
